    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>XEOM: Saigon Edition</strong> drops you into the bustling heart of Saigon, where you become a motorbike taxi driver zipping through narrow alleys, dodging traffic, picking up passengers, delivering packages, and avoiding all sorts of obstacles!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a taxi rider In the heart of Sai Gon</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on a variety of delivery missions and earn your keep</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase upgrades, unlock new riders and keep your bike refueled</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge oncoming traffic and finesse your way around the many wacky obstacles on Sai Gon roads</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover iconic landmarks: Independence Palace, the glamorous Bui Vien street and Ben Thanh market</p></li></ul>",
